                    h3 Declaration of BTC AG on data protection
                    p
                        | Data protection and data security for customers and users have a high priority for BTC. The protection of your personal data in
                        | all our business processes is therefore of particular concern to us.
                    p
                        | This privacy statement explains what information is collected on our website during your visit and how this information is used.
                        | However, this declaration does not apply to websites of other companies that contain a link to this website of BTC AG or to which
                        | our website has provided links.
